    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/376afb8b0ec73c99cf7251f8350dffdf.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/376afb8b0ec73c99cf7251f8350dffdf.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/376afb8b0ec73c99cf7251f8350dffdf.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>分段世界，独特的标签行动</strong><br>在分段世界中，每个阶段都有两个背景作为Segment并存。 每个背景将双胞胎的区域分开。 您可以通过片段标记字符，并使用每种攻击方式。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/ce26d01311db4874f4230ce97b9aa4a3.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/ce26d01311db4874f4230ce97b9aa4a3.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/ce26d01311db4874f4230ce97b9aa4a3.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Mush Hunter 双胞胎，“Matilda”和“Amanda”</strong><br>她们是双胞胎女孩，她们是靠与 Mush 战斗为生的猎人。 两个双胞胎女孩分别拥有“Sword Master”和“Gunslinger”的攻击方式。<br><br><br><strong>时尚、击球手感</strong><br>该游戏采用经典街机格式，节奏快。 在不断的战斗中你可以感受到良好的打击感。<br><br><br><strong>卡通风格</strong><br>它具有模仿漫画外观的独特图形，包括halftone和glitch效果。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/76753f6c3934804fabca8b0e82e5fc1c.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/76753f6c3934804fabca8b0e82e5fc1c.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/76753f6c3934804fabca8b0e82e5fc1c.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>各种 Mush 和诱人的 5 个 Boss</strong><br>打倒阻碍双胞胎少女的Mush，打倒压倒性的BOSS！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/9f4bc97890b102dde3c7bf82c304e266.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/9f4bc97890b102dde3c7bf82c304e266.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/9f4bc97890b102dde3c7bf82c304e266.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
